      "slide_or_page": 52,
      "element_type": "text_box",
      "element_id": "slide_52_Rectangle_2",
      "source_text": "Many functions will seek to enforce policies and procedures through forcing stakeholders to conform to these\nMany functions also attempt to create a Gatekeeper role to attempt to control flows of information between stakeholders and external suppliers\nImproved results are achieved through engaging with stakeholders to seek commitment to achieve sources of added value - this approach underlines the advisory/consultant role of the function\nConsider the links the function has internally and externally\n- Where are the internal links? are they positive and collaborative?\n- What could you do to understand the external links?",
      "character_count": 626,
      "is_in_text_box": true,
      "is_in_table": false,
      "layout_context": "Shape: Rectangle 2",
      "translation_status": "PENDING",
