      "slide_or_page": 54,
      "element_type": "text_box",
      "element_id": "slide_54_Rectangle_2",
      "source_text": "The function can attempt to influence the different tiers of a supply chain.\n- How can this be achieved?\nThe more remote the tier, then generally the more difficult it will be to exert influence.\nWhy is the case? And what are the potential risks & impact?\nIn the same way that different internal customers exert conflicting interests on us, the dynamics of a supply chain are even more complicated, so to exert real influence is always difficult.",
